    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The show was cancelled - but behind-the-scenes is a harrowing plot designed to destroy lives in the name of profit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spirits and other creatures now lurk the abandoned set, leaving you unsure of who to trust.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate the set, learn the truth behind the closure of the show, and try to escape once and for all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253140/extras/a1fb5bb44a5db2684121c7c1218f918f.poster.avif?t=1763528463\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253140/extras/a1fb5bb44a5db2684121c7c1218f918f.webm?t=1763528463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253140/extras/a1fb5bb44a5db2684121c7c1218f918f.mp4?t=1763528463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desperate to escape the abandoned set, you strike a deal with a creepy android that is a replica of the star's show - Mint herself. You  agree to search the set for its lost power cores.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armed with special ghost-hunting tools, you must navigate the haunted remnants of the set, discovering cryptic hints and recovering the android's missing pieces.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you collect all the hints and reactivate Android Mint before time runs out?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253140/extras/b87031d48c1e1e14040a12ac10af1a03.poster.avif?t=1763528463\" width=594 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253140/extras/b87031d48c1e1e14040a12ac10af1a03.webm?t=1763528463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253140/extras/b87031d48c1e1e14040a12ac10af1a03.mp4?t=1763528463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Hours of Playtime</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ghost Hunting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obstacle Courses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cart Racing</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lore &amp; Story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VHS Cutscenes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voice Acting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Made in Unreal Engine</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253140/extras/bb6739a7b37524e4be7054700117feee.poster.avif?t=1763528463\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253140/extras/bb6739a7b37524e4be7054700117feee.webm?t=1763528463\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253140/extras/bb6739a7b37524e4be7054700117feee.mp4?t=1763528463\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
